title: Introduction to CNN and its Use for Image Classification
description: On 28th September 2021, IEEE-DBIT Student Branch organized a hands-on workshop on 'Introduction to Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and its Use for Image Classification. The session commenced by Ajitha Rajkumar(IEEE-DBIT-Chairperson), addressing the participants and welcoming the speaker, Dr. Bhakti Vilas Baheti to deliver the talk. Comparisons of various CNN Architectures were done with respect to size,accuracy, and parameters.
